{{vgname2|水箭龜|ja=カメックス|en=Blastoise}}是[[任天堂|任天堂]]和[[Game_Freak|Game Freak]]所特許經營的《[[精靈寶可夢系列|精靈寶可夢]]》系列裡的虛構生物「[[寶可夢列表|寶可夢]]」之一，在《[[精靈寶可夢_紅·綠|精靈寶可夢 紅]]》與《[[精靈寶可夢_紅·綠|精靈寶可夢 綠]]》中首次被引入，並出現在該系列的後續作品及改編作品中。它的外型是一隻背上搭載[[水槍|水槍]]的巨龜。

== 設計 ==
水箭龜由Game Freak團隊設計、由[[杉森建|杉森建]]定稿，是第一世代的151種寶可夢之一<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/interview/irbj/vol1/index2.html |title=2. 一新されたポケモンの世界 |page=2 |work=Nintendo.com |publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo]] |accessdate=2010-09-10 |author=Staff |language=ja |archive-date=2018-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623165950/https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ds/interview/irbj/vol1/index2.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=91965 |title=Game Freak on Pokémon! |author=Stuart Bishop |publisher=CVG |date=2003-05-30 |accessdate=2008-02-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5VSJaR6xT?url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=91965 |archivedate=2008-02-08 |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>。水箭龜是該世代初學者寶可夢之一[[傑尼龜|傑尼龜]]的最終進化型態，龜殼上有兩個可以射出水柱的砲管，體型也比先前更加壯碩。

==登場==
=== 在電子遊戲中 ===
水箭龜初次登場於《精靈寶可夢 紅》和《精靈寶可夢 綠》，並出現在《皮卡丘》、《火紅》、《葉綠》及主系列的後續版本中，以及《精靈寶可夢彈珠檯》、《寶可夢益智方塊》等作品。自《精靈寶可夢 X》和《精靈寶可夢 Y》起，水箭龜可以使用超級進化<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pokemonxy.com/en-us/pokemon/mega_pokemon/ |title=Mega Pokémon |publisher=Pokemonxy.com |date=2013-09-04 |accessdate=2013-09-04 |archive-date=2015-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150810155941/http://www.pokemonxy.com/en-us/pokemon/mega_pokemon/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為了讓玩家可以體驗到水箭龜（以及噴火龍、妙蛙花）的超級進化，才將傑尼龜（以及小火龍、妙蛙種子）加入遊戲中<ref>{{cite web |title=Pokemon X/Y: WHY?! Director Masuda himself answers! |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/pokemon-xy-why-director-masuda-himself-answers/ |work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |last=Betka |first=Zach |date=2013-09-19 |accessdate=2014-03-16 |archive-date=2014-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140317041640/http://www.gamesradar.com/pokemon-xy-why-director-masuda-himself-answers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

=== 動畫 ===
在[[精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)|動畫]]裡，擁有水箭龜的訓練家並不多，其中之一是大木茂，他在啟程時選擇傑尼龜做為初學者寶可夢後，隨著故事進展而進化成水箭龜<ref name="The Ties That Bind">{{cite episode| title =けっしょうトーナメント！フルバトル６VS６!! | series = [[精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)|精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)]] | credits =冨岡淳廣 | network =  | airdate = 2002-10-10 | season =|number = 270}}</ref>，該水箭龜與小智的噴火龍在白銀大會的對決被視為經典對決之一<ref>{{cite news |title=寶可夢經典決戰！　水箭龜輸噴火龍..倒地前竟罵「靠北」？ |url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20160910/772960.htm |language=zh-tw |author= |publisher=Ettoday |date=2016-09-10 |accessdate=2018-04-19 |archive-date=2018-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180419183439/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20160910/772960.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。水箭龜最初登場於無印第17集，一個具有大量機器寶可夢的島上<ref name="Island of the Giant Pokémon">{{cite episode| title =きょだいポケモンのしま!?| series =  [[精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)|精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)]]  | credits =首藤剛志 | network = | airdate = 1997-07-22 | season =|number = 17}}</ref>，真正的水箭龜出現在無印第59集，胖丁卡住水箭龜的砲管，導致後者沉睡不醒<ref name="Beach Blank-Out Blastoise">{{cite episode| title =カメックスのしま | series =  [[精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)|精靈寶可夢系列_(動畫)]]  | credits = 冨岡淳廣 | network =  | airdate =  | season = |number = 59}}</ref> 。

=== 漫畫 ===
在《[[神奇寶貝特別篇|神奇寶貝特別篇]]》中，小藍從大木博士的研究所偷走傑尼龜，這隻傑尼龜最後進化成水箭龜，並成為小藍隊伍的主力之一<ref name="Zap! Zap! Zapdos!">{{cite book |last=秀憲 |first=日下 |author2=真斗 |title=VSサンダー |series=[[神奇寶貝特別篇|神奇寶貝特別篇]] |volume=3 |date= |publisher= |isbn=|chapter=30}}</ref>。它具有用噴射水槍造成的反作用力快速移動的能力。

==迴響==
IGN稱水箭龜「非常受觀迎」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://faqs.ign.com/articles/380/380983p1.html |title=Pokemon Crystal Version Pokemon of the Day: Jolteon (#135) – IGN FAQs |publisher=Faqs.ign.com |accessdate=October 17, 2011 |archive-date=2012-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009160939/http://faqs.ign.com/articles/380/380983p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的編輯布雷特·艾爾斯頓（Brett Elston）認為水箭龜「酷斃了」且「有訓練的價值」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/wii/f/the-complete-pokemon-rby-pokedex-part-1/a-200708209459101025/g-2006100415372930075/p-7 |title=The complete Pokemon RBY pokedex, part 1, Pokemon Black / White Wii Features |publisher=GamesRadar |accessdate=October 17, 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322065013/http://www.gamesradar.com/wii/f/the-complete-pokemon-rby-pokedex-part-1/a-200708209459101025/g-2006100415372930075/p-7/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他比較水箭龜、噴火龍和妙蛙花後指出噴火龍以龍的造型走「大眾路線」，而水箭龜則是「獨一無二」<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.gamesradar.com/ds/f/the-complete-pokemon-rby-pokedex-part-1/a-200708209459101025/g-2006100415372930075/p-9 |title= The complete Pokemon RBY pokedex, part 1, Pokemon Diamond / Pearl DS Features |publisher= GamesRadar |author= Brett Elston |page= 9 |accessdate= 2018-04-19 |archive-date= 2016-04-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160414195426/http://www.gamesradar.com/ds/f/the-complete-pokemon-rby-pokedex-part-1/a-200708209459101025/g-2006100415372930075/p-9/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。[[UGO_Networks|UGO Networks]]稱水箭龜為「狠角色」<ref>{{cite web |author=UGO Team |url=http://www.ugo.com/the-goods/blastoise |title=Blastoise |publisher=UGO.com |date=July 23, 2010 |accessdate=October 17, 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829150029/http://www.ugo.com/the-goods/blastoise |archivedate=August 29, 2012 |df= }}</ref>。[[GamePro|GamePro]]認為很多玩家是出於那兩根大砲管而選擇水箭龜<ref>{{cite web|last=Bailey |first=Kat |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/218621/wtfs-up-with-you-guys-and-pokemon/ |title=WTF's up with you guys and: Pokemon, Feature Story from |publisher=GamePro |date=March 26, 2011 |accessdate=October 17, 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/218621/wtfs-up-with-you-guys-and-pokemon/&date=2011-11-30+18:58:29|archivedate=2011-11-30}}</ref>[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的派翠西亞·赫南德茲（Patricia Hernandez）認為水箭龜的超級進化是最糟糕的超級進化之一，評論「呃……它有了更大的砲管，但還是用嘴噴出破壞死光？」<ref>{{cite web |title=The Best and Worst of the New Mega Evolutions In Pokémon X & Y |url=http://kotaku.com/the-best-and-worst-of-the-new-mega-evolutions-in-pokem-1446514749 |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |last=Hernandex |first=Patricia |date=2013-10-16 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-date=2014-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140604020609/http://kotaku.com/the-best-and-worst-of-the-new-mega-evolutions-in-pokem-1446514749 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[官方任天堂雜誌|官方任天堂雜誌]]》把它列為第四佳的水屬性寶可夢<ref>{{cite web |title=Best Water Pokemon |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/35298/best-water-pokemon/?page=2 |page=2 |work=[[Official_Nintendo_Magazine|Official Nintendo Magazine]] |last=East |first=Thomas |date=2012-02-10 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415112024/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/35298/best-water-pokemon/?page=2 |archive-date=2014-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。ONM的寫手湯瑪斯·伊司特（Thomas East）把水箭龜列為最酷的寶可夢之一，他稱水箭龜是足以與噴火龍並駕齊驅的水屬性寶可夢<ref>{{cite web |title=Top 10 cool Pokemon that aren't Legendary |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/44935/cool-pokemon/?page=7 |work=[[Official_Nintendo_Magazine|Official Nintendo Magazine]] |last=East |first=Thomas |date=2012-12-17 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008004555/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/44935/cool-pokemon/?page=7 |archive-date=2014-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]]的亞歷克斯·奧斯本（Alex Osborn）把水箭龜列為有史以來最佳寶可夢的第十名<ref>{{cite web |title=21 Greatest Pokémon of All Time |url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/features/7-greatest-pokmon-of-all-time#/slide/12 |page=12 |work=Game Revolution |last=Osborn |first=Alex |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-date=2014-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408041317/http://www.gamerevolution.com/features/7-greatest-pokmon-of-all-time#/slide/12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

